freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I am being treated for colitis and my husband pointed out that the sudden emptying of my colon (not diarrhea) was probably a result of the vaccine. It was once. There was no pain or repeat. I thought I would mention in case useful information. We both feel very good and are grateful.
